Program: Discovery
Title: Saving the brain
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry50
Last Broadcast Date: 30 July 2002
How advances in surgery are helping those with brain injuries or tumours. The programme looks at surgery and head injuries. A brain tumour sufferer describes the process of an awake craniotomy. Presenter unknown. Producer: Rami Tzabar.